  "detailed_description": "Dear Citizen, you have been selected to test drive the new Tether Tech Roller™. This is an experimental vehicle designed for non-linear travel by means of cutting edge Roll, Jump, Swing and Glide technology. With the Tether Tech Roller™ technology you can Roll, Jump, Swing and Glide seamlessly, at great speeds! Complete deliveries faster and earn more points while driving the Tether Tech Roller™!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nROLL<br />\r\nGenerate torque and boost along the ground at great speeds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJUMP<br />\r\nConvert speed to height using the leg spring approach favoured by gymnasts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSWING<br />\r\nTether to any surface and combine with boost and look direction to fling across the map. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGLIDE<br />\r\nGain height and glide over long distances converting height for speed for tremendous acceleration.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCOMBINE <br />\r\nUsing all the features together there is no limit to what you can accomplish in the Tether Tech Roller™!",
  "about_the_game": "Dear Citizen, you have been selected to test drive the new Tether Tech Roller™. This is an experimental vehicle designed for non-linear travel by means of cutting edge Roll, Jump, Swing and Glide technology. With the Tether Tech Roller™ technology you can Roll, Jump, Swing and Glide seamlessly, at great speeds! Complete deliveries faster and earn more points while driving the Tether Tech Roller™!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nROLL<br />\r\nGenerate torque and boost along the ground at great speeds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJUMP<br />\r\nConvert speed to height using the leg spring approach favoured by gymnasts.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSWING<br />\r\nTether to any surface and combine with boost and look direction to fling across the map. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGLIDE<br />\r\nGain height and glide over long distances converting height for speed for tremendous acceleration.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCOMBINE <br />\r\nUsing all the features together there is no limit to what you can accomplish in the Tether Tech Roller™!",
